class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed228c82db8e4c9fcb02e09784badde11d2ab84","tid":1344454,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162193097230245/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FTaipoTaipo%2Fpermalink%2F10162193097230245%2F&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=81e539a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/TaipoTaipo/permalink/10162193097230245/</a><br />\n<br />\n而香港人需要人幫助嘅時候，點解係要我哋自己幫自己？</blockquote><br />\n呢個世界不嬲都咁運作架啦柳生<br />\n<br />\n我想買樓果陣，唔通李生會幫我地咩"},{"pid":"37c163b550051ab47494f6451c547447923f7aaf","tid":1344454,"uid":276558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:58:15.000Z","msg":"喊撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7c3d0115c72470959ec06575eefbfdb81a4d02","tid":1344454,"uid":28257,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:00:18.000Z","msg":"我相信，今晚之後，唔會有再有咩民意論，淺藍該變黃的會早就變左，全香港人都會歸邊企。我地亦唔需再花時間精力，黎勸告班深藍或者中立派黎歸邊。<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地呢班人，除左係網上發表D偉論之外，一無是處，除非有錢收，佢地亦唔會自行集結起黎，形成一股可對抗/打擊抗爭者的勢力。佢地無行動力，無號召力，佢地只會做樹立制度者的順民，唯一的分別係，做舊有制度定係新制度的順民。</span><br />\n<br />\n元朗地鐵流傳影片之中，有一幕，一位男士跪左係到求班白衣唔好再打人，佢甚至幫白衣拎返起副眼鏡，結果下場係一拳打面。<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地用行動講左比我地知，求和平只會求委屈。</span>我地宜家係訓左係地下，頭比人用腳踩著，一啖一啖口水吐緊落塊面到。"},{"pid":"953771cc723c380791e5adbea494077b3365b84e","tid":1344454,"uid":130162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoCgyu1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoCgyu1.png&h=c83ce221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf2ef7e3ad504c5a110c7680c11e6bc42411caf5","tid":1344454,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\